article.headline: Askew scores 16, Long Beach State takes down Cal State Fullerton 73-56
article.description: — Devin Askew's 16 points helped Long Beach State defeat Cal State Fullerton 73-56 on Thursday.
article.linkText: Askew scores 16, Long Beach State takes down Cal State Fullerton 73-56
article.story: FULLERTON, Calif. -- — Devin Askew's 16 points helped Long Beach State defeat Cal State Fullerton 73-56 on Thursday. Askew had six rebounds and three steals for the Beach (2-8, 1-0 Big West Conference). Kam Martin scored 11 points while going 4 of 8 (3 for 6 from 3-point range). TJ Wainwright shot 4 for 10 to finish with 10 points. The Beach ended an eight-game slide with the win. Kendrick De Luna finished with 10 points for the Titans (2-7, 0-1). CSU Fullerton also got nine points and seven rebounds from Kobe Young. John Square Jr. finished with nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
